#

Hearty Lentil Vegetable Soup

45 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodSoupHealthy

Description

A comforting and nutritious lentil soup packed with vegetables and flavors, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • green or brown lentils: 1 cup
  • carrots: 2, diced
  • celery: 2 stalks, diced
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • tomatoes: 1 can (14 oz), diced
  • bay leaf: 1
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • thyme (dried): 1 teaspoon
  • parsley (fresh or dried): 2 tablespoons
